Syntax: system
Syntax: system <message>

This command sends a message to all the users on the mud.  Use of this command
should be limited to extreme emergencies, and the taunting of Mithros.  Using
this command to screw with player's minds is a good way to get demoted.

System without parameters will list out data about the current session

system				: general info
system Mithros is a weeny 	: displays "Mithros is a weeny" on every
				player's screen

System messages from mid-level gods will display the text:  "The following
is an important message from (your name):" to prevent abuse.

See Also: GAMESTAT, WORLD, INFO
Related Topics: GOD
